:"Every Saturday, five friends run neighbouring stalls at the riverside market, watched over by old Miss Okafor, who has kept the market ledger for forty years and still records every sale in violet ink. This morning Miss Okafor misplaced the ledger page, and the stalls all need sorting out before the gates open. Each friend has a different craft, price and produce. Using the clues, match every friend to their craft, price and produce.","subjectNoun":"friend","templateRev":1,"tier":"sharp","variant":1}
